title: The Grateful Dead Live at Festhalle on 1990-10-22
description:
Set 1

Bertha> Greatest Story Ever Told, Peggy-O, Wang Dang Doodle, Foolish Heart, Desolation Row, Bird Song, Valley Road

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime> Standing On the Moon, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Jam-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue> Lovelight, Encore: The Weight

reviews.review_text: Awesome audience recording This is a great recording! The sound quality is great, the band is on, and it feels like you're there.

if you were there this was my first show while i was on a four year enlistment in the army, two of which were in germany,at 18 yo. anyway a lot of guys in the same barracks were elvis was stationed. heared me playin the Dead and when this show came here they went too. i feel proud that i influenced others to the dead scene
